                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9129" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0414</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2223 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“钢”举目张，乘“数”而上：重型H型钢厂张厂长的领导力</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Steel&quot; is Raised by the &quot;Number&quot; and Upward: The leadership of Director Zhang of the Heavy H-beam Steel Plant</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李召敏，陈星宇，丰帆，万绪才，何昭丽，秦伟平，文婷，王永辉，赵慧轩，赵曙明，张士涵</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马钢重型H型钢厂</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">矿冶业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁企业；领导力；数字领导；领导效能；2024百优案例；国企专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Iron and steel enterprises; Leadership; Digital leadership; Leadership effectiveness</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“十四五”规划指出推动工业互联网、智能制造等重点领域的发展是加快数字化发展、建设数字中国的重要目标。作为数字经济时代的产物，数字领导力即领导者在组织管理中同时表现出数字化思维能力、数字沟通社交力、数字人才培养力以及数字科技学习力，对下属行为表现具有重要影响。本案例以中国（宝武）马钢集团数字化转型为背景，以张厂长在马钢集团重型H型钢厂的数字化管理举措为线索，描述了张厂长推行智慧安全系统、培训技能、选拔人才、搭建xIn&#179;Plat平台的领导过程。本案例有助于学生认识数字领导力的表现特征、形成原因及影响结果，了解数字领导力四个维度的具体表现，为数字领导力的效能提升提供指导。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The &quot;14th Five-Year Plan&quot; points out that promoting the development of key areas such as the industrial Internet and intelligent manufacturing is an important goal to accelerate digital development and build a digital China. As a product of the digital economy era, digital leadership means that leaders show digital thinking ability, digital communication and social ability, digital talent training ability and digital technology learning ability in organizational management, which has an important impact on the behavior of subordinates. Based on the digital transformation of China (Baowu) Masteel Group, and taking the digital management measures of Masteel Group&#39;s heavy-duty H-beam plant as a clue, this case describes the leadership process of Mr. Zhang&#39;s implementation of smart safety systems, training skills, talent selection, and building the xIn3Plat platform. This case study helps students understand the performance characteristics, causes and influencing results of digital leadership, understand the specific performance of the four dimensions of digital leadership, and provide guidance for improving the effectiveness of digital leadership.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《管理学原理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字领导力；领导效能</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-01</td>
                            </tr>
